-- AIG decides not to join Greenberg suit against government: WSJ
-- 
-- Wed Jan 9, 2013 2:51pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/01/09/us-aig-lawsuit-decision-idUSBRE90814Z20130109

 

 (Reuters) - American International Group Inc will not join a lawsuit against the U.S. government challenging the terms of the insurer's 2008 bailout, the Wall Street Journal reported on Wednesday, citing unnamed sources. 
 AIG had said its board was meeting Wednesday to consider the possibility of joining the suit filed by former CEO Hank Greenberg. (Reporting by  Ben Berkowitz ; Editing by  Gary Hill )